ing nothing in return.  On a side note one member of their team also made me a steel breast plate and just gave it to me.  He made me promise though, that once I out grow the breast plate that I must give it away to another in need and not sell it.  If nothing else, I thank you Malinki, Coldari, Parin, and Avihenda.<br>
<br>
&quot;Sometimes losing can teach you things about yourself; I'm not there yet but I hope that someday I will be.&quot;<br>
